text: Sasha Feldman is an American actor. He was the main character, Gabe, in Confessions of a Teenage Jesus Jerk (2017). He had a role, as "Bliz", in Get Shorty (TV series) (2017).Sasha Feldman, at IMDB He was born in Baku, Azerbaijan, and came to the U.S. as a young child. ==References== Category:American male film actors Category:American male television actors Category:21st-century American male actors Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
